reviewText: Not false advertising, but not what you expect given the titles;  neither movie is the identically titled Disney version and neither is anywhere near as good as the Disney versions. But two stars because not awful, and the two together were cheap.
I would only rate this item as average because I bought it for my niece's  pleasure.
Not Disney but good stories of Little Mermaid & Pocahontas. It is fun to see the same story from different companies
